<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Erud's Tonic Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Goto Hawk's Inn in Erudin and purchase the drink "Innoruuk's Kiss of Death"<BR>
<BR>
2) Take this drink to Sinnkin Highbrow on the top floor of the library.<BR>
<BR>
3) You will recieve an Erud's Tonic, which is required for several quests.</div>
